---
import Skelet from "../layout/skelet.astro";
---

<Skelet>
  <style>
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .mission {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        border-bottom: 0.5px solid #1e1e1e;
      }
      .title {
        margin-left: 15px;
        /* margin-right: 50px;
        flex-shrink: 0; */
      }
      /* .about {
        border-bottom: 0.5px solid #1e1e1e;
      } */

      .mission_img img {
        width: 250px;
        height: auto;
        padding-left: 2%;
        padding-right: 20%;
        /* padding-bottom:20px; */
        /* border-bottom: 0.5px solid #1e1e1e; */
      }

      .cocohanne_img img {
        width: 100%;
        display: block;
        margin: 0 auto;
        border-top: 0.5px solid #1e1e1e;
        border-bottom: 0.5px solid #1e1e1e;
        padding-top: 15px;
        padding-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .history_container {
        border-bottom: 0.5px solid #1e1e1e;
        border-top: 0.5px solid #1e1e1e;
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
      .mission-container {
        flex: 1;
        /* padding-left: 10px; */
        border-left: 0.5px solid #1e1e1e;

        margin-left: 10px;
        width: 100%;
      }
      .culture_container {
        /* display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start; */
        border-bottom: 0.5px solid #1e1e1e;
      }
      .culture_container .title {
        margin-right: 50px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }

      .mission-container,
      .culture-container p,
      .history_container p {
        padding-left: 5%;
        padding-right: 5%;
      }
    }
    @media (min-width: 600px) {
      .mission {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        border-bottom: 0.5px solid #1e1e1e;
      }
    }
  </style>
  <div class="about"></div>
  <h1>About</h1>

  <div class="history_container">
    <div class="title">
      <h2>History</h2>
    </div>

    <p>
      Alpha is an artist management agency dedicated to supporting and promoting
      emerging talent in the music industry. Founded with a vision to create
      more space for alternative music in Denmark and beyond, Alpha focuses on
      empowering artists and helping them reach new audiences both domestically
      and internationally.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mission">
    <div class="mission_img">
      <img src="/imgs/mission.png" alt="a picture of the founders" />
    </div>

    <div class="mission-container">
      <h2>Mission</h2>
      <p>
        One of our key missions is to foster diversity within the Danish music
        scene by championing up-and-coming artists and providing them with the
        resources and support they need to thrive. Whether it's through artist
        services, event management, or strategic partnerships, Alpha is
        committed to driving growth and innovation in the industry.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="culture-container">
    <div class="title">
      <h2>Culture</h2>
    </div>
    <p>
      Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed do eiusmod
      tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim
      veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea
      commodo consequat.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="cocohanne_img">
    <img
      src="/imgs/cocohanne.png"
      alt="Coco and Hanne, the founders of Alpha"
    />
  </div>
</Skelet>
